OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPaul Simon 'beginning to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Faccept' hearing loss       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Paul Simon has said he is "beginning   
OL,6, to" accept his hearing loss, and that  
OL,7, having such a disability "changes how  
OL,8, you interact with life" and work.      
OL,10,FThe US singer-songwriter, 81, revealed 
OL,11,Fin May that he had almost completely   
OL,12,Flost hearing in his left ear.          
OL,14,FThe Hollywood Reporter quoted him on   
OL,15,FSunday saying: "I haven't accepted it  
OL,16,Fentirely, but I'm beginning to."       
OL,18,FHe was speaking after the premiere of  
OL,19,FIn Restless Dreams: The Music of Paul  
OL,20,FSimon at the Toronto Film Festival.    
